00:17:03.020 --> 00:17:06.900
But these are details, right?

00:17:06.900 --> 00:17:09.260
No, there's a
reasonable question.

00:17:09.260 --> 00:17:10.740
How hard would you have to pull.

00:17:10.740 --> 00:17:13.473
Of course, if we want,
